<topic id="classId" xml:lang="en-us">
<title>Medication Activity - conformance rules</title>
<shortdesc id="shortdesc">[SubstanceAdministration: templateId <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.24</tt>]</shortdesc>
<prolog id="prolog">
<metadata><category>SubstanceAdministration</category></metadata>
<resourceid id="2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.24"/>
</prolog>
<body>
<ol id="conformance">
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.doc/classes/SubstanceAdministration.html">CDA Substance Administration</xref></li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain [1..*] <tt>id</tt></li>
<li><b>SHOULD</b> contain [0..1] <tt>statusCode</tt></li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain [0..1] <tt>entryRelationship</tt> such that it<ol>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <xref href="../MedicationSeriesNumberObservation.dita">Medication Series Number Observation</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.46</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain [0..1] <tt>entryRelationship</tt> such that it<ol>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <xref href="../MedicationStatusObservation.dita">Medication Status Observation</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.47</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain [0..*] <tt>entryRelationship</tt> such that it<ol>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] @typeCode="SUBJ" <i>SUBJ (has subject)</i></li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <xref href="../PatientInstruction.dita">Patient Instruction</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.49</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> satisfy: <codeblock>self.moodCode=vocab::x_DocumentSubstanceMood::EVN or self.moodCode=vocab::x_DocumentSubstanceMood::INT </codeblock></li>
</ol>
</body>
